{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"75044fc1cb","title":"在中央常委会上的四点指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"69b26017c6","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"75044fc1cb","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"干部和干部政策","id":"3df4ae75e1","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4a8928dcdd","type":"title","text":"在中央常委会上的四点指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75044fc1cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7abe89350b","type":"paragraph","text":"在中央常委会上的四点指示","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75044fc1cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f747cf4e77","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75044fc1cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5e7c274026","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.01.00","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75044fc1cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"29851bc6a7","type":"paragraph","text":"（1） 大家要挺身而出，同群众见面，接受群众的批评。要进行自我批评，引火烧身。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75044fc1cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d8f0678010","type":"paragraph","text":"（2） 大家要挺身而出，向群众解释党的政策，被戴高帽子，抹了黑脸的，洗洗脸继续上班工作。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75044fc1cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"13f3f62ef7","type":"paragraph","text":"（3） 从长远利益出发，团结多数。牛鬼蛇神就是地、富、反、坏、右，是少数。有些人就是犯了严重错误，也得挽救他，使他改过自新，不然怎么团结百分之九十五以上呢？","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75044fc1cb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a5283de26","type":"paragraph","text":"（4） 说服干部，使干部懂得不要人人过关，都搞得灰溜溜的。两个挺身而出，不能躲躲闪闪，怕字当头。敢字当头，再大的问题也能解决。怕字当头，价钱越来越高。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75044fc1cb","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}